title: Simple check of summary health state of HP BladeSystem Enclosures
agents: snmp
author: Lars Michelsen <lm@mathias-kettner.de>
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the summary health of HP BladeSystem Enclorures.
 The check uses the state information reported by SNMP. Addionally to the
 reported state the firmware version and the serial number are shown in
 the check output.
 On windows systems, some versions of the Proliant tools seem to report 
 a status of "Other" which triggers an UNKNOWN status.

inventory:
 One check per enclosure is created automatically.
